  "title": "Two cylindrical white UFOs observed in Curitiba [2000]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/14/two-cylindrical-white-ufos-observed-in-curitiba-2000/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-s7",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>AUG 12th, 2000</strong>. Time: 19h15pm. Duration: 10 minutes. In the Champagnat neighborhood in the city of Curitiba, State of Paraná, a witness spotted two small unidentified flying objects in the form of a white &#8220;cartridge&#8221;. According to the report, the UFOs were separated by a distance of 4,000ft between them and moved in the East / West direction at a slow speed and at an estimated altitude of 10,000ft. The sighting was made, according to the witness, under good visibility conditions, with &#8220;scattered clouds&#8221; being noted at the observation site.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.582. “</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Questionário sobre avistamento de ovni no bairro de Champagnat em Curitiba, Paraná”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n",
  "excerpt": "<p>AUG 12th, 2000. Time: 19h15pm. Duration: 10 minutes. In the Champagnat neighborhood in the city of Curitiba, State of Paraná, a witness spotted two small unidentified flying objects in the form of a white &#8220;cartridge&#8221;. According to the report, the UFOs were separated by a distance of 4,000ft between them and moved in the East [&hellip;]</p>\n",
